Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咪撚玩啦 唔開營利撚有錢咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢冇開廣告姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> youtube會跟views數比錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好似係廣告分紅？無開廣告你一億views都無錢收<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌你老母，唔明啲人點解會支持，偷人野又講撚到幫佢吸引多啲人睇，同backup佬啲支持者有乜分別。唔想做義工咪唔好做囉，講到幫佢哋做翻譯好似益左原創者，木下/香港啲youtuber都搵fans幫自己整字幕，youtube已經有呢個功能，想做翻譯咪幫佢地個channel做咪得囉，有無錢就另一件事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢同backup佬有分別。分別就係在於佢地有翻譯，而翻譯依個行為的確可以增加作品嘅受眾。起碼比單純backup多。<br />\n問題只係在於原作者嘅想法。<br />\nBackup佬嘅問題係在於達哥名言唔想佢backup。之前無講一樣無人覺得佢有問題。"},{"pid":"38ff8ca298cd26bc622020179c5e4a134c893bc9","tid":313454,"uid":23021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T12:17:16.000Z","msg":"Youtube無廣告姐<br />\n佢咁多sub開facebook開blog<br />\n上面大撚把廣告啦"},{"pid":"7dced6ec6fe984862a942470db5ee24869dea495","tid":313454,"uid":13309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T12:19:09.000Z","msg":"好多都有授權，對原作都有利"},{"pid":"cd9798c92e80a7c7fc47bf149fda6973d3401f7f","tid":313454,"uid":1977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T12:20:35.000Z","msg":"無左佢地我返工都無乜意義啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc0c816e7d31ac4c1ce72c35ffccf70cba4f69e9","tid":313454,"uid":39287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T12:22:04.000Z","msg":"拉登咪又係抄人   咪又係唔洗比人ban<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5a97b81a0affbf9aadffeff4d1843ff4617a3ae","tid":313454,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T12:24:49.000Z","msg":"依個翻譯page喺我初中已經有<br />\n幾分鍾嗰啲短片係做得幾好既<br />\n但係長啲嗰啲就好撚垃圾 (eg last week tonight)<br />\n<br />\n不過話分兩頭<br />\n你估翻譯好易咩?<br />\n英文廢啲都未必識聽啦<br />\n更何況普遍台仔啲英文廢既程度同支那